THIS PROJECT CAN RUN ONLY ON LINUX SYSTEMS 
To run this project locally on the your computers make sure you are connected to the internet and you have downloaded both the python files init.py and app.py
Create a new directory and copy these two python files and paste them in the new directory.
Now make sure you have python on your systems, so open your terminal and type python3 --version and if no error pops up then you have python installed on your systems.
Now first run init.py to install required modules , to run it type python3 init.py and hit enter. In this the terminal will ask you for your password to install ffmpeg , a necessary package and then press y after entering your password.
After init.py successfully runs then type python3 app.py and then work accordingly.

